productList.description: Inspired by a vintage slip dress from the roaring ’20s, this striking little number is embroidered with allover sequins in a scalloped pattern. A removable rose brooch enhances the glamorous art-deco-inspired mood. Counter the opulence with cool moto boots for an unexpected finish.

Designed to turn heads, this V-neck dress features ruched, ’80s-inspired sleeves and is embellished in light-catching sequins. Balance its opulence with polished flats, adding a hoodie for a cool yet unexpected finish.

A show-stopping piece for city days or weekend parties, this dress is extravagantly embroidered with sequins and beads in a paisley motif. The scalloped hem is finished with beaded fringe that adds drama and movement. Counter its glamour with cool moto boots and a leather jacket.

This dress knows how to make an entrance. Cut in a figure-skimming silhouette with bell cuffs, it’s covered in paved sequins for an all-out glamorous effect. Style it with a colored clutch and platform heels to create the ultimate party look.

A glamorous alternative to your favorite LBD, this mockneck dress is designed in stretch-viscose with metallic dots that deliver subtle shimmer. The slinky silhouette is accentuated with a twist detail at the hip, while smooth lining ensures a sleek fit. Complement its shine with silver-tone accessories.
Designed in a textured diamond pattern knit with metallic threads, this dress features a classic crew neckline and bell cuffs. Pair it with eye-catching accessories.

The ubiquitous little black dress, with a twist. This long-sleeve version is cut from ribbed stretch-viscose for an ultra-flattering fit and is embellished with smooth studs at the neckline and cuffs. Consider it your new go-to for work, parties and everywhere in between.

A striking choice for black-tie affairs, this jumpsuit is cinched at the waist and features a mesh bodice embroidered with sequins in a baroque-style pattern. Keep emphasis on the detailing with noir accessories.

Cast in lightweight georgette with a detachable slip, this shirtdress is updated in a tie-neck silhouette punctuated by tonal embellishments. Style it with slouchy boots for a day-to-evening look that’s effortlessly fabulous.

This long-sleeve dress is a flattering pick for daytime or an evening out. Rendered in lightweight georgette, it’s textured in a miniature dot jacquard pattern with foil edges for subtle shine. The flirty silhouette showcases a wrap-effect bodice with a ruffled skirt and smocked detailing at the waist and cuffs.
Glistening sequins take this simple shift dress from low-key to luminous. Cut from lightweight jersey, it looks best styled with embellished loafers and a leather satchel.

A sophisticated take on the LBD, this version is tailored in a shift silhouette with understated puff sleeves and cascading ruffle details on the front. Accessorize it with an embellished clutch and loafers for refined around-the-clock style.
A feminine silhouette and mixed rose prints combine to romantic effect on this georgette dress. Detailed with flutter sleeves and a ruffled hem, it’s a flirty choice for any event on your calendar.

Designed in the season’s key rose print, this tie-neck dress is crafted from airy georgette with an attached lining and sheer sleeves. Elastic detailing at the cuffs and waist balance the relaxed silhouette, while a ruffled hem adds a touch of femininity. Wear it for a night out with an embellished belt and ankle boots.

The effortless slip dress is reimagined this season in velvet devoré that’s highlighted by a romantic rose print. Complement the midi hemline with platform sandals and finish with a faux fur jacket for an extra layer of texture.

Rendered in velvet devoré, this tactile dress is designed in the season’s winter rose print. Soft ruffles frame the neckline, while a removable oversized belt defines the waist. Keep it in focus with noir extras.

Defined by a mini rose print, this jumpsuit delivers instant style with minimal effort. It’s cast in a wide-leg silhouette crafted from airy georgette and complete with a coordinating sash to cinch the waist. Take it from 9 to 9 with minimalist sandals and a structured shoulder bag.

Cast in airy georgette, this belted shirtdress showcases a graphic chevron print and blouson sleeves that complement the fluid silhouette. Finish with leather extras for around-the-clock sophistication.

Meet the dress that’s perfect for both seasonal soirées and romantic date nights. Corded floral lace and an exaggerated shoulder detail strike a couture note, while sheer sleeves add a touch of allure. Wear it with a faux fur coat and richly textured accessories, adding a belt to highlight the waist.

A luxe choice for after-dark affairs, this dress is crafted from velvet devoré and features an abstract swirl pattern. A detachable tank slip offers full coverage while leaving a sheer finish on the shoulders and décolletage. This flattering A-line silhouette is complete with a ruched bust and flutter sleeves for a touch of romance.

Faceted metallic studs punctuate this belted matte-jersey dress with standout shine and texture, while scalloped detailing adds art deco appeal. Team it with combat boots and an embellished bag for a luxe downtown-inspired statement.

Light-catching metallic embroidery and sparkling stones combine to glamorous effect on this lace dress. It features a tiered skirt with scalloped edges that evoke an art-deco-inspired sensibility. For an extra dose of drama, team it with an opulent crossbody and ankle boots.

This party dress is sure to steal the spotlight at any evening soirée. A glittering scallop-print lends art-deco-inspired glamour, while a draped back detail and chain accent ensure this silhouette will make an equally striking exit.

This fit-and-flare dress is flocked with a velvet diamond motif that’s punctuated by touches of glitter. Wear it to your upcoming holiday event with barely-there sandals and an equally luxe shoulder bag.

This sleeveless dress is rendered in rose lace with tonal embroidery for added texture and features an understated collar with delicate ties. Consider it an elegant choice to wear on sunny afternoons or for evening affairs.

This dress channels romantic elegance in rose lace construction with delicate appliqués. It features an opaque tank lining that leaves the neckline and shoulders exposed for alluring contrast. Counter the femininity with easy espadrille sandals.

Rich in tactile appeal, this short-sleeve dress is intricately embroidered with delicate florals, lacquered sequins and pretty eyelet details. It’s complete with an opaque slip that promises full coverage but leaves the neckline and shoulders exposed for alluring contrast.
This dress evokes a romantic sensibility in floral lace construction with a suntan-colored lining. Pair it with a satchel and minimalist sandals for an effortlessly luxe look.

Meet the jumpsuit that will take you from work to weekend and everywhere in between. Rendered in lightweight georgette, this short-sleeve style features an understated keyhole at the neckline and a wrap-effect bodice with a knotted detail to define the waist. Balance the wide leg with platform sandals.

This dress is destined to be a mainstay in any 9-to-5 wardrobe. Cut from stretch viscose in a flattering fit-and-flare shape, it’s detailed with a V-neckline, understated puff sleeves and ribbed trim. Complete the look with a structured satchel and point-toe pumps.

Sleek and streamlined, this midi dress is knit from ribbed stretch-viscose for a second-skin fit. Sparkling stones outline the silhouette with subtle shine and offer an added dose of texture. Wear it by day with cool trainers, switching to platforms come evening.
Contrasting logo tape brings this mockneck dress into the here and now, while a ribbed knit ensures a sleek and streamlined look. Channel a cool downtown attitude with a belt bag and combat boots.

Cut from curve-hugging jersey, this easy midi dress is defined by a thigh-grazing side slit and twist detail at the waist. Pair it with heels and metallic accessories for added glamour on your next dinner date.
A flattering option for daytime or date night, this long-sleeve bodycon dress is crafted from stretch-viscose with a belted waist. A leather satchel and ankle boots refine the look.
Sleek and streamlined, this V-neck midi dress is crafted from a figure-flattering stretch fabric while a ribbed waist lends a textured touch. This alluring LBD is your ticket to after-hours style.
Defined by shimmering plaid jacquard, this dress showcases a flattering wrap-effect front and smocked waist. We love how the airy georgette fabric and ruffled hem add romantic movement.

Made to flatter in a textured stretch-knit, this fit-and-flare dress features understated ruching at the shoulders and a ribbed waist detail. Endlessly versatile with polished character, count on it to take you from work to weekend and beyond.

Light up the room in this striking party dress. Crafted from gold silk jacquard, the scalloped motif stands out against the cordovan underlay. Sheer flutter sleeves, a cinched waist and ruffled hem finish the silhouette on a feminine note.

Cut from diaphanous georgette with a tiered hem, this halter dress features a sequined collar and rose brooch that channels the season’s ’20s glamour. Style it with noir sandals and a ladylike bag for after dark.
Feather embroidery adds an opulent finish to this otherwise classic wool-blend dress. Bring it into statement-making territory with equally striking boots.

Neatly crafted from smooth cady, this V-neck shirtdress is designed to flatter with a cinched waist and features covered buttons for a polished finish. Consider it a sophisticated option for every day.

This dress is an elegant choice for any evening affair. Crafted from corded lace in an intricate rose garden pattern, it’s complete with an attached lining and romantic scalloped hem. Make color your focus and finish with accessories in coordinating hues.
